lead_paragraph: Joseph Schooling won the men's 100 metres butterfly final on Friday to secure Singapore's first Olympic gold medal and deny Michael Phelps a 23rd in the last individual race of the American's extraordinary career.

headline.main: Swimming-Schooling Wins First Gold for Singapore
headline.print_headline: Swimming-Schooling Wins First Gold for Singapore
